```

## Key Metrics

| Metric | Target |
|--------|--------|
| Content freshness | < 90 days |
| TTFB | < 200ms |
| LCP | < 2.5s |
| Information retrieval | Core facts extractable |
| Topic coverage | Complete coverage |

**Remember**: SEO is a tool. The real goal is revenue, not traffic. Always focus on conversion and user value.
